article_title: Missing Your Emu? The Sarasota County Animal Services May Have It
article_text:
If you're in Florida and you can't find your emu, the Sarasota County Sheriff's Office would like to hear from you.

This week, after a large bird was spotted wandering near a highway, the animal services department posted the following message to their Facebook:

"Him/her?" That might also be something to investigate. Either way, come get your bird back!
